  "comment": "BTS250C LED Profile Spot Zoom 250W RGBW: The BTS250C is powered with a 250W 4-in-1 high power LED with manual zoom and is designed to replace traditional profile spot lights. The 18° - 36° all-in-one zoom range covers the most regular 19°, 26°, 36° lenses. A rainbow of colours in a single 250W LED profile spot. The whole fixture is enclosed in a robust ABS housing featuring four metal framing shutters, gobo slot and is supplied with filter frame and safety cord.\n\n",
